divs: Sighting DetailsI saw the object at approximately 23:10, however earlier in the day I was grilling around 18:00 and my dogs were highly agiated and riled up and kept charging my backfence and barking then quickly retreat back to me wimpering I thought nothing off it originally until they kept picking up on something I looked and saw nothing so if finished my food ate and left for a friends I returned approximately 23:10 And as I pulled into my driveway I noticed a very bright rectangle in the sky about halfway up the height of a cellphone tower just remaining stationary and I thought too myself I don't remember there being a tower in that direction. I park my truck get out and my dogs are still howling and highly agiated still wondering if what I saw was a cell tower an I saw nothing no light nothing I looked at every angle to find this thing but I saw nothing.
